data.description: Re-modeled and on the golf course!  Move in ready with new carpet & vinyl flooring, fresh paint throughout, new GRANITE in kitchen, cabinets with new paint, deck stained and overlooking the 10th hole. First floor master with cathedral ceiling.  Newer HVAC and sealed crawlspace. Community golf, pool, and fitness center.
data.whatILove: Golf course lot backs up to chipping green with view of main club house. Nice yard. Deck.  Laundry room.  Walk in attic.  Large master.  Large master closet.  Sinks separate from bathroom. Bay windows. Granite, new carpet and vinyl, tile floor in half bath. Garden tub in master bath.  Wrapped and sealed crawl space.  HVAC 4 years old.  Nice neighbors.
